                <h1>Emma Watson: Actress & Activist</h1>
                <p>Emma Watson is an accomplished actress and activist, best known for her role as Hermione Granger in the Harry Potter series. Beyond acting, she advocates for gender equality and sustainable fashion. Emma is also a UN Women Goodwill Ambassador, inspiring global audiences with her dedication to social change and empowerment.</p>
